and even people of ques-</div><div class="t md32 x63 h51 ycc2 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tionable reputation, including some who had been violent per-</div><div class="t m1289 x63 h51 ydff ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">secutors. Having experienced His saving power, they all be-</div><div class="t m163f x63 h51 y1637 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">came His special ambassadors. </div><div class="t mde x3f h51 y618 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Today Christ is calling men and women from all walks of </div><div class="t m2c0 x63 h51 y2ed ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">life to join Him in the greatest challenge ever committed to </div><div class="t m5c2 x63 h51 y1cbf ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">humankind—the work of spreading the exciting news that, by </div><div class="t me53 x63 h51 y1ba1 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accepting Jesus Christ as Saviour and Lord, all may enjoy </div><div class="t mebe x63 h51 y1c50 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eternal life with Him. </div><div class="t m1ba0 x3f h51 y9dc ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Everyone in whose heart Christ abides, everyone who will </div><div class="t mdd5 x63 h51 ya1f ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">show forth His love to the world, is a worker together with </div><div class="t m2eb x66 h51 y1cab ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God for the blessing of humanity. As he receives from the </div><div class="t m63f x66 h51 y107b ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Saviour grace to impart to others, from his whole being flows </div><div class="t m1350 x63 h51 yfbf ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forth the tide of spiritual life.&quot;—The </div><div class="t mdc3 x76 h3b yd4d ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Acts of the Apostles, </div><div class="t m875 x19f h51 y14e0 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 13. </div><div class="t m117c x66 h51 y132a ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
